The channel airs Nicktoons, as well as acquired programming from outside providers. Unlike the United States version, it has been ad-supported since launch. 

Therefore, "Nicktoons exlcusively airs Nicktoons and programming from Nickelodeon" is guaranteed, possible, or impossible?

Therefore, ""Be Right Back" has existed for over 6 years" is guaranteed, possible, or impossible?

Assume it is true that Club Atlético Unión de Mar del Plata is an Argentine sports club from Mar del Plata, Buenos Aires Province. The club was founded on December 1, 1926, and its main sports are football and basketball. In football, Unión currently plays in the Torneo Argentino A, which is the regionalised third division of the Argentine football league system. 

Therefore, "Club Atlético Unión de Mar del Plata has been around for 100 years" is guaranteed, possible, or impossible?

The Bantiger TV Tower was built between 1991 and 1996 as replacement of a 100 metres tall radio tower, built in 1954. 

Therefore, "Bantiger TV Tower is used for AM-, FM-, and TV-transmissions.  " is guaranteed, possible, or impossible?

The tour began on August 9, 2009, and ran until July 30, 2010, after a run of shows in Japan, and visited North America, Europe and Oceania. The tour was in support of the band's debut album.

Therefore, "George Avakian is no longer living." is guaranteed, possible, or impossible?

Assume it is true that The Queen, often referred to as the Evil Queen or the Wicked Queen, is a fictional character and the main antagonist in "Snow White", a German fairy tale recorded by the Brothers Grimm; similar stories are also known to exist in other countries. Other versions of the Queen appear in "Snow White" derivative works, and the character has also become an archetype for unrelated works of fiction.
